OL,3,CCar production fell last month,
OL,4,Cfigures show
OL,6,FCar production fell back last month as
OL,7,Ffactories adjusted for new models,
OL,8,Flatest figures show.
OL,10,FThe number of cars built was 59,467,
OL,11,Fdown by 27% compared with a year ago,
OL,12,Fsaid the Society of Motor
OL,13,FManufacturers and Traders (SMMT).
OL,15,FIt was the first fall since August
OL,16,Flast year but the trade body said it
OL,17,Fwas in line with expectations for a
OL,18,Fvariable year, as manufacturers adjust
OL,19,Ffactories to produce the next
OL,20,Fgeneration of cars, notably electric.
