OL,3,CCar production fell last month,
OL,4,Cfigures show
OL,6,FVolumes for the UK fell by 0.3% to
OL,7,F19,995 units, while production for
OL,8,Fexport was down by 35.9% to 39,472
OL,9,Funits, although more than six in 10
OL,10,Fcars made in March were shipped
OL,11,Foverseas.
OL,13,FThe European Union received the bulk
OL,14,Fof exports (57.9%) followed by the US
OL,15,F(11.4%), China (5.9%), Australia
OL,16,F(4.0%) and Japan (1.8%).
OL,18,FElectrified vehicle (battery electric,
OL,19,Fplug-in hybrid and hybrid) models
OL,20,Fagain represented more than a third of
OL,21,Fall production.
