OL,3,CCar production fell last month,
OL,4,Cfigures show
OL,6,FCar production remained up 1.1% in the
OL,7,Ffirst quarter, at 222,371 units,
OL,8,Fcompared with the same period a year
OL,9,Fago.
OL,11,FSMMT chief executive Mike Hawes said:
OL,12,F"This fall is not unexpected given the
OL,13,Fwholesale changes taking place within
OL,14,FUK car factories as existing models
OL,15,Fare run out and more plants transition
OL,16,Fto electric vehicle production.
OL,18,F"We can expect further volatility
OL,19,Fthroughout 2024 as manufacturers lay
OL,20,Fthe foundations for a successful zero
OL,21,Femission future.
