OL,3,CCar production fell last month,
OL,4,Cfigures show
OL,6,FThe latest independent production
OL,7,Foutlook now expects UK car and light
OL,8,Fvan production to fall 6.2% to around
OL,9,F940,000 units this year, mainly due to
OL,10,Fmultiple model changeovers, before
OL,11,Freturning to growth in 2025, said the
OL,12,FSMMT.
OL,14,FOutput is anticipated to get back
OL,15,Fabove a million units from 2026 and
OL,16,Freach 1.2 million before the end of
OL,17,Fthe decade as more EV production comes
OL,18,Fon stream.
